data.description: Northbay Home on 1 Acre! 3 bedroom + 2.5 bath + additional bonus rooms + shops. Vaulted ceilings with open-concept living/dining areas. Spacious bonus room can be used for home office or media room. Main floor laundry room with extra storage. Upstairs primary suite has ensuite bath & walk-in closet. 2 more bedrooms and guest bath. 2 car garage, 3rd high bay garage great for any mechanic! Private entrance on the side of the house to a motorcycle garage that could also be used for workout space or workshop. Air compressor piped to both garages included. Numerous fruit trees, pen for chickens, outdoor shed & garden space. Within walking distance to Northbay!
